202
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:42,640
Xiao Yao,

203
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:46,120
I did badly,

204
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:47,680
making you suffer so much,

205
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,520
making you wait alone for so long.

206
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:53,440
But from now on,

207
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,160
I will always be by your side,

208
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,800
